[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0081","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0081.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0097","title":"Microsoft Index Server 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Microsoft Index Server 2.0 及 Windows 2000 Indexing Service 中的 WebHits ISAPI 筛选器存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的畸形 Hit-Highlighting 参数请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows 2000 及安装了 Index Server 2.0 的系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。攻击无需身份认证，利用难度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0097"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:59.673","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS00-006 提供的官方补丁：Index Server 2.0 用户下载 Intel 或 Alpha 平台对应补丁（https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?FamilyID=87BCE044-43FD-470E-8CAC-C2B51BEC872A），Windows 2000 Indexing Service 用户下载补丁（https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?FamilyID=61AA188B-07F4-430D-877A-8C68D7AAF47D）。如无法立即打补丁，可暂时禁用 WebHits ISAPI 筛选器（_vti_bin/..%5c..%5c..%5c..%5c 路径过滤）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1210","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/950","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-006","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19731","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/94380d498cb52b65d051c9bd443b6f2aa85bf8ec/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0097.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0097","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0097.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cdbbe57bd34c799f670485304ef54912650bf03b/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0097.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-726j-722q-69g3/GHSA-726j-722q-69g3.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2008/remote-MS00-006.nasl","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/ms_index_server.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0097.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0081.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0114","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0114.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0126","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0/4.0 示例 IDQ 脚本目录遍历漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 及 4.0 中自带的示例 Internet Data Query（IDQ）脚本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向服务器发送包含 ..（点点）序列的特制 HTTP 请求，利用 IDQ 脚本绕过虚拟目录路径限制，读取服务器上任意文件（如系统配置文件、ASP 源码等）。该漏洞源于 IDQ 脚本未对用户输入的文件路径参数进行充分过滤，影响 Windows NT 4.0 Option Pack 默认安装的 IIS 服务器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0126"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-26","updated":"2000-01-26","remediation":"删除 IIS 安装目录下 /Scripts/ 文件夹中的示例 IDQ 脚本文件（如 iisadmin.idq、iissamples.idq 等），或升级至不再包含示例脚本的 IIS 版本。对于 Windows NT 4.0 系统，建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统以获得安全更新支持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0126","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19742"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0114.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0079","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0079.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0095","title":"HP-UX 路径最大传输单元发现拒绝服务漏洞","description":"HP-UX 10.30 和 11.00 版本中的路径最大传输单元（PMTU）发现过程存在缺陷，当系统接收到特制的小尺寸数据包时会产生大量响应流量，从而被远程攻击者利用作为数据包放大器，造成拒绝服务（DoS）放大攻击。攻击者无需认证即可通过网络远程触发此漏洞，主要影响系统的可用性，导致网络带宽被耗尽或服务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0095"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-24","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"HP 已发布针对该漏洞的补丁：HP-UX 10.30 安装补丁 PHNE_20880，HP-UX 11.00 安装补丁 PHNE_20892。如无法立即打补丁，可临时关闭 PMTU 发现功能，执行 ndd -set /dev/ip ip_path_mtu_discovery 0 或在 ndd 中将 ip_ire_pathmtu 设为 0，并限制外部 ICMP 不可达报文入口作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/944","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/advisory.html?id=2041"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0079.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0306","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0306.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0093","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10768,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10789}}","description":"Red Hat Linux 系统在安装过程中使用基于 DES 算法的 crypt() 函数对初始账户密码进行加密存储，而非更安全的 MD5 算法。由于 DES 加密仅取密码前 8 个字符参与运算，导致弱密码防护与哈希碰撞风险。该漏洞影响安装时采用默认加密方式的 Red Hat Linux 发行版，本地或具备读取密码文件权限的攻击者可通过暴力破解或字典攻击轻易还原用户口令，进而提升权限或横向移动。利用方式通常为获取 /etc/shadow 或 /etc/passwd 后针对 DES 哈希进行离线破解。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0093"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:59.167","remediation":"升级到 Red Hat Linux 6.2 及以上版本，安装 shadow-utils 与 pam 相关更新包（如从 Red Hat 安全公告获取的修复 RPM），并修改 /etc/pam.d/passwd 与系统认证配置，将密码加密方式由 crypt() 的 DES 改为 md5 或 sha512；同时使用 `authconfig --passalgo=md5` 重置加密算法，并对现有账户执行 `passwd` 强制重设密码以迁移哈希。临时缓解可将 /etc/login.defs 中 ENCRYPT_METHOD 设为 SHA512 并限制口令文件访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0093","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e358b3016d8b52194aa099dc1255ebe1441bbafa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0093.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0093","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/5239f9720650b7a54642c185fed8488a4f9c4ead/2000/CVE-2000-0093.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0093.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jpmj-rq8m-mfq3/GHSA-jpmj-rq8m-mfq3.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/94e644a0057439310dc2677c2e4ebd7766be1682/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0093.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88231/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/2c2d199ea4b93fdae34a0d5271ea75e4cd24739e/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0306.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0300","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0300.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0091","title":"Inter7 vpopmail (vchkpw) 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Inter7 vpopmail 的 vchkpw POP3 认证组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 POP3 端口发送特制的超长用户名或密码数据包触发栈溢出，成功利用可在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 vpopmail 3.4.11 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0091"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-01-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:58.910","remediation":"立即升级 vpopmail 至 3.4.12 或更高版本，该版本已修复 vchkpw 认证模块中用户名/密码长度未校验导致的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，可在 tcpserver 或 xinetd 层限制 POP3 认证请求的用户名字段长度不超过 64 字节，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.inter7.com/vpopmail/","http://www.inter7.com/vpopmail/ChangeLog","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/942","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19727","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/83494e95424aced4cfc65648b3019774f7fc51c3/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0091.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0091","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0091.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/03324c0426abad4e55ae7c73b0bba67b9c87e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0091.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j7gx-8wqm-phgg/GHSA-j7gx-8wqm-phgg.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/pop3_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001112.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0091.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0300.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0098","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0098.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0115","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10779,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10797}}","description":"Microsoft IIS 在处理包含 Visual Basic Script 的 ASP 页面时，VBScript 引擎对脚本中使用的正则表达式（RegExp 对象 Pattern 属性）缺乏有效校验，当传入非法或不完整的正则表达式时，VBScript 运行时（vbscript.dll）会触发访问违例（Exception C0000005），导致承载 Web 服务的 Inetinfo.exe 进程崩溃，从而引发拒绝服务。攻击者须具备在服务器上创建或修改 ASP 页面的本地权限，通过在 ASP 页面中写入含无效正则表达式的 VBScript 代码并请求该页面，即可触发服务崩溃，使 IIS 停止响应所有 HTTP 请求。该漏洞主要影响 Windows NT 4.0 Enterprise 上运行 Service Pack 6 及 6a 版本 IIS 的系统。Microsoft 后续通过安全更新修复了 VBScript 引擎对正则表达式的异常处理机制，建议受影响用户及时安装补丁并限制本地用户的 ASP 页面写入权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0115"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:01.897","remediation":"建议将 Microsoft IIS 升级至 Windows 2000 Service Pack 1 或安装微软 2000 年 2 月发布的安全更新（MS00-008），以修复 VBScript 正则表达式处理缺陷。如无法立即升级，可在 IIS 管理控制台中取消匿名用户对存放 ASP 页面的虚拟目录的执行权限，并仅允许受信任用户访问，同时限制本地普通账户对 Web 目录的写权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94881904724731&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/73dad9db65989a09e468a4f3a98f0eea36f0346c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0115.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0115","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/4bcbd71189dce529293f66e955a23227152461d0/2000/CVE-2000-0115.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0115.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5pfw-hvfc-h744/GHSA-5pfw-hvfc-h744.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0115.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88274/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001114.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0098.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0073","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0073.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0088","title":"Microsoft Office Word/PowerPoint 文档转换器缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Office 套件中的文档转换工具在处理日语、韩语及中文 Word 5 格式文档时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，即\"格式转换数据异常\"漏洞。未经身份验证的远程攻击者可构造特制的畸形文档，诱使用户使用 Office 或相关转换工具打开该文件，即可触发缓冲区溢出并在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Word、PowerPoint 等 Office 组件及 Office 转换工具包，攻击者利用该漏洞可实现远程代码执行，完全控制受影响的系统。攻击条件为攻击者需要诱骗用户打开恶意构造的文档文件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0088"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:58.527","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS00-002 补丁（KB249881），将 Microsoft Word 97/98/2000、PowerPoint 97/2000 及 Office Converter Pack 2000 的日文、韩文、中文版本升级至修复版本。建议通过 Windows Update 或 Microsoft 下载中心获取 Word 5 文档转换工具补丁程序；如无法立即安装补丁，可暂时禁用或卸载 Office 中的 Word 5 格式转换功能作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/946","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-002","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7cda0b7fa75f17f1e2b56ef076a6f9175f854ab4/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0088.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0088","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0088.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4cacb08131e7c4736ad136de17873dbcaeddf850/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0088.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v953-3rp8-5v5v/GHSA-v953-3rp8-5v5v.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c0675c79-afb8-42ff-adb6-ddd71d517e29.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0088.json","https://github.com/aboutcode-org/aboutcode-mirror-euvd/blob/b7580d6aba8040c22f37d85dec61d19c97d13189/advisories/2022/04/EUVD-2000-0087.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0073.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0071","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0071.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0086","title":"Netopia Timbuktu Pro 明文传输用户名与口令漏洞","description":"Netopia Timbuktu Pro 是一款远程控制与桌面共享软件。该软件在远程会话认证过程中，以明文形式在网络上传输用户名和口令，未采用任何加密保护机制。攻击者在网络链路中实施嗅探（如 ARP 欺骗或共享介质监听）即可截获凭据，进而冒充合法用户获得对目标主机的远程控制权限。攻击条件为攻击者能够访问目标与客户端之间的通信链路。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0086"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-20","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级到已修复凭据传输加密的 Netopia Timbuktu Pro 新版本；在网络层启用 SSH 隧道或 VPN 加密链路，避免明文凭据在不可信网络中传输。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T06:48:27.090204447+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0086","https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2000-0086"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0071.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0076","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0076.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0092","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9124,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10810}}","description":"BSD make 程序在 -j 选项下存在符号链接攻击漏洞，本地用户可通过精心构建的符号链接在并行执行过程中非法修改关键文件。该漏洞影响所有使用 BSD make 构建工具的 Unix 系统，导致权限提升和文件破坏。攻击者需具备本地访问权限并触发并行构建作业方可利用此漏洞，已确认对系统完整性和可用性构成严重威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0092"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:59.043","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 系统至 2000-01-16 之后的版本，或应用 FreeBSD-SA-00:01 补丁：以 root 执行 `cd /usr/src/usr.bin/make && patch < /path/to/patch/file && make all && make install`，将临时文件创建方式从静态文件名改为 mkstemp() 安全随机生成。临时缓解措施：避免使用 `make -j` 并行编译选项。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/939","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8981d7e7baa3f6c5d7a90cd823433b0422b8fcd2/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0092.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0092","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0092.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/94e644a0057439310dc2677c2e4ebd7766be1682/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0092.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-vcw7-xgh4-9m7m/GHSA-vcw7-xgh4-9m7m.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0092.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/2c2d199ea4b93fdae34a0d5271ea75e4cd24739e/2000.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--94960d45-3530-49d5-82c9-b52791f833d8.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0076.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0074","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0074.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0089","title":"Microsoft Windows 注册表枚举文件信息泄露漏洞","description":"CVE-2000-0089 是 Microsoft Windows 系统中注册表相关组件存在的漏洞，攻击者在已获得本地或远程访问权限的情况下，可利用该漏洞枚举注册表中存储的文件相关信息，从而获取系统配置、安装路径及敏感文件位置等数据。该漏洞主要影响 Windows NT 等系统的注册表访问机制，攻击条件为攻击者需具备一定程度的系统访问能力，利用后可辅助进一步的特权提升或信息收集。建议尽快安装微软发布的安全补丁以消除该风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0089"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-19","updated":"2000-01-19","remediation":"安装微软发布的对应安全补丁（如 Windows NT 4.0 SP6a 及后续更新），限制注册表远程访问权限，并通过 ACL 收紧对注册表项的访问策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T07:55:21.606945516+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0089","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/929"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0074.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0083","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0083.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0099","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16272,\"outputTokens\":42,\"totalTokens\":16314}}","description":"UnixWare 操作系统自带的 ppptalk 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该命令在处理用户输入的提示参数（prompt argument）时未对输入长度进行边界校验，导致本地用户可通过构造超长的提示参数触发缓冲区溢出，进而覆盖栈上返回地址并执行任意代码，最终以 root 等高权限账户身份运行恶意指令，实现本地权限提升。攻击条件为攻击者需先获得目标系统的本地普通用户访问权限，并在本机执行 ppptalk 命令并传入精心构造的长参数。此漏洞影响使用存在缺陷版本的 UnixWare 系统，CVSS 基础评分 7.2，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0099"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:59.913","remediation":"立即安装 SCO 官方针对 UnixWare ppptalk 缓冲区溢出发布的安全补丁（如 ptf 系列补丁），或升级至已修复的 UnixWare 版本（建议 7.1.2 及以上）。如暂无法打补丁，可通过 chmod 700 /usr/bin/ppptalk 限制普通用户执行权限，并将该命令属主设为 root、仅授权管理员使用，同时移除非必要用户的本地登录与 shell 访问权限以缓解提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00